<div class="contaier">
  <div class="row d-md-flex d-lg-flex no-gutters">
    <div class="col-lg-5 order-sm-1 order-lg-0 order-md-1 home-bg-img">
      <h1 class="logo-text">MR  RED  NECK</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-7 order-sm-2 order-lg-2 order-md-2">
      <div class="create-coctail-btn text-center mt-5">
        <%= link_to 'Create Cocktail', new_cocktail_path, class: 'btn btn-ghost' %>
      </div>
      <div class="covid-update-card">
        <div class="card-news">
          <h2>Covid Update</h2>
          <p>Our team are taking a break because of Covid.</p>
          <p>We will announce here once we re-open!</p>
          <p>Until then keep drinking in your home.</p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> And never forget <span>1.5m</span> <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></p>
          <p> 🍺 🍻 🥂 🍷 🥃 🍸 🍹 🧉 🍾 🧊</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <% @cocktails.each do |cocktail| %>
            <div class="col-lg-6 card-container">
              <div class="card m-2 card-style">
                <% cocktail.photo.attached? ? @image = "//res.cloudinary.com/apak/image/upload/#{cocktail.photo.key}": @image = cocktail.image_scr %>
                <img class="card-img-cocktail" src="<%= @image %>" alt="Card image cap">
                  <div class="card-body"> 
                    <h5 class="card-title"><%= cocktail.name %></h5>
                    <%# <h5 class="card-title"><%= cocktail.rating %></h5>
                    <%= link_to 'View Cocktail', cocktail_path(cocktail), class: 'btn btn-ghost' %>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          </div>
          <div id="about">
          <h2 class="text-center" id="title">About Us</h2>
            <p id="about-parag">We wanted to say thank you for the support you've shown us during this long 2020.
              We are back open to the public so please pop in, grab a drink and say hi. 
              During the next few weeks we will still be able to do take-aways for your trips to the park or to collect Sparrow’s.
              The fridge is still full of plenty of goodies, that change weekly. So come and pick something different to share.
              Stay safe and drink beer. </span>
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
